ActPublic Service Employment Act
PrecisAppointment of EMŐKE J. E. SZATHMÁRY, C.M., O.M., of Winnipeg, Manitoba, to be a special adviser to the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness, to serve as a member of the Interim Management Advisory Board for the Royal Canadian Mounted Police, to hold office during pleasure for a term of eighteen months, on a part-time basis.
